title: Assault Cube1.1.0.4 (Portable)
description:
AssaultCube is a Free, first-person shooter game with very low system requirements. It is a small but good game which you can play offline or Online (Multiplayer).

This is a portable version of AssaultCube, no installation required. Just download and play.


System requirements
----------------------------------------------------------
Processor:	Intel Pentium III or AMD K7 range

GFX:		NVIDIA GeForce 256 or ATi Radeon R7000

RAM:		192 MB
----------------------------------------------------------

Offical website of AssaultCube http://assault.cubers.net/
